-- Ex-Cerberus Managing Director Settles Suit Against Firm
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2013-05-24T17:23:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-24/ex-cerberus-managing-director-settles-suit-against-firm.html
Lisa Marie Vioni, a former managing
director at Cerberus Capital Management LP, settled a lawsuit
over her claims that she was wrongfully terminated after trying
to correct what she called misleading marketing materials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
